{
  "texts": [
    "Determining the structure and explicitly evaluating several criteria is crucial.",
    "Therefore, constructing and resolving multicriteria planning and decision-making challenges is referred to as MCDM.",
    "As a result, MCDM is composed of a set of numerous criteria, a set of alternatives, and some sort of comparison between them [18][19][20].No alternative optimizes all criteria uniformly in multicriteria optimization assignments.",
    "Any solution to the multicriteria task that enhances a specific criterion can be examined, but the task must ultimately have a preferred option.",
    "The decision maker must provide more details to select the best decision."
  ]
}